'''Hweru''' (Aardvark or antbear in English) imhuka yemusango ine muromo murefu neganda rinenge renguruve inochera zimwena zihombe pasi. Hweur kana kuti '''Hwiribidi''' inowanikwa mu[[Africa]] chete.

==Tsika==

Munguva yehondo yerusununguko kune muimbi akaimba rwiyo rwaikurudzira varwi verusununguko rwainzi, "Hwiribidi famba nepasi, nyika dzekwedu inyika dzemvura".

